(version 1)

# Phase 1 Cycle 8 custom DRC rules file.
#
# NOTE: the `hole_clearance` waiver originally planned here was
# replaced by a board-level min_hole_clearance relaxation from
# 0.25 mm to 0.15 mm in claude-code-pad.kicad_pro. See
# DESIGN-NOTES.md Cycle 8 for the rationale (JLCPCB basic-tier
# 2-layer HASL-LF manufacturability spec). KiCad 10 custom DRU
# rules do not override the board-level hole_clearance rule in the
# direction of relaxation (they can only tighten, not loosen), so
# the relaxation must be set at the project level.
#
# This file is retained for future fine-grained rules if needed.
